## 🕹️ Gamification Rules

Every feature must incorporate game mechanics:

- **Streaks**: Daily prayer streak with flame icon. Displayed prominently everywhere.
- **XP System**: Each prayer = XP. Display XP gain with a floating "+XP" pop animation.
- **Levels**: Users level up. Level badge shown on profile.
- **Achievements / Badges**: Unlockable badges (e.g., "7-Day Streak", "First Fajr", "Ramadan Warrior").
- **Progress Tracking**: Visual progress rings for daily 5 prayers.
- **Leaderboard**: Weekly leaderboard with animated rank changes.
- **Quests**: Daily/weekly challenges (e.g., "Complete Fajr 3 days in a row").

Every reward moment (prayer completion, badge unlock, level up) must trigger a **celebration animation**.

