## 📱 Component Standards

### Button Component
Every button MUST follow this pattern:
```tsx
// Always 3D pressed effect, rounded, with loading state
<Button variant="primary" | "secondary" | "ghost" | "danger" size="sm" | "md" | "lg" loading={false} />
```

### Card Component
- Rounded corners (`--radius-lg`)
- Colored left border accent or full colored background variants
- Hover: subtle lift animation

### Progress Ring
- SVG-based circular progress for prayer tracking
- Animated stroke-dashoffset on mount and update

### Streak Display
- Flame icon with glow effect
- Counter with bounce animation on increment

### Prayer Time Card
- Shows prayer name, time, countdown
- Color changes based on current/upcoming/passed state
- Pulsing indicator for the active prayer

---

## 🌙 Feature-Specific Rules

### Prayer Times
- Fetch using Aladhan API or similar
- Use geolocation for automatic city detection
- Display all 5 prayers in a visually engaging horizontal or card layout
- Countdown timer to next prayer — animated

### Streak System
- Persist in localStorage + backend sync
- Visual streak flame grows with streak length (CSS scale)
- Streak freeze mechanic (like Duolingo's streak freeze)

### Learning Module (Wudu, Prayer Steps)
- Step-by-step animated guides
- Mascot demonstrates each step
- Progress through steps like a game level

### Ramadan Mode
- App theme shifts to `--color-ramadan` palette during Ramadan
- Special UI: moon/star motifs, lantern animations
- Iftar countdown = most prominent element
- Suhoor alarm setting with animated clock

### Notifications
- Use Web Push API
- Notification UI within app: toast-style with mascot icon
- Settings page to control which prayers to get notified for

