## 🚫 Forbidden Patterns

- ❌ No plain white/gray corporate UI
- ❌ No generic system fonts (Arial, Inter, Roboto)
- ❌ No static screens — every screen must have at least one animation
- ❌ No `any` in TypeScript
- ❌ No inline styles (use CSS modules or Tailwind consistently)
- ❌ No direct DOM manipulation — use React patterns
- ❌ No hardcoded strings — use i18n from day one (the app will support Arabic, Turkish, English)
- ❌ No components longer than ~150 lines — split and compose
- ❌ No API calls directly in components — always go through a service layer / React Query hook
- ❌ No `useEffect` for data fetching — use React Query
- ❌ Never animate `width`, `height`, `top`, `left`, `margin` — use transforms only

---

## ✅ Checklist Before Every PR / Feature

- [ ] Component is reusable and lives in the right feature folder
- [ ] TypeScript types are properly defined — no `any`
- [ ] Animation is present and respects `prefers-reduced-motion`
- [ ] Uses design tokens (CSS variables) — no hardcoded colors or sizes
- [ ] Mobile-first responsive design
- [ ] Loading state is handled (skeleton / spinner)
- [ ] Error state is handled with user-friendly UI
- [ ] Empty state is handled with mascot illustration
- [ ] i18n keys are used for all user-facing strings
- [ ] Accessibility: keyboard navigable, ARIA labels on interactive elements

